 <p>Windows 7 and Windows Live bring it all together for <strong>free</strong>. Get the free set of programs that make it simple to create and share amazing photos and movies, organize mail, and stay connected with your closest friends.</p>
 <ul>
 <li><strong>Get free online storage</strong> with Windows Live SkyDrive. </li>
